      <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4"><a href="#gallery" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-400/30 text-cyan-200 hover:bg-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-400/60 transition-all duration-300 text-sm">Explore Gallery</a>
